      "description": "# PDF to MD Converter Plugin - v1.0.2\r\n\r\n## Initial Release\r\n\r\n- **PDF Conversion**: Convert PDF files to Markdown format using the Marker API\r\n- **Image Extraction**: Option to extract and save images from PDFs\r\n- **Metadata Handling**: Ability to write PDF metadata as YAML frontmatter in the resulting Markdown file\r\n- **Folder Management**: Options to create a new folder for converted files\r\n- **File Overwrite Protection**: Checks for existing files and asks for user confirmation before overwriting\r\n- **User Interface**: \r\n  - Adds a command to Obsidian's Command Palette and file-menu for easy access\r\n  - Implements custom dialogs for user interactions during the conversion process\r\n- **Settings**: Customizable plugin settings for tailoring the conversion process",
